    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Introduction"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We can see Clock monitor cyclically checks AG2i_STDBY registers and in case of any failure it will trigger a SMU SW alarm ALM10[0]"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Why is this needed?"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "IFX recommends to cyclically monitor AG_STANBY registers."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "SM[HW]:CLOCK:ALIVE_MONITOR"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Monitor the activity of the following clocks"
    },
